sm.setSpeakerID(1022002)
sm.sendSayOkay("The boy didn't say a word about what he saw. He simply stated his name, Jin, before leaving with the former Dark Lord's lifeless body. And that was it. Since then, I have not heard a thing about the boy or the former Dark Lord. Tristan will always be remembered for sacrificing his life to seal Lord Balrog, and here I am... I've told you all that I know. Now go, I'm feeling tired... If you have anything else to say, why don't you go talk to that daughter of his...?")
